high_descs: Move to the toilet roll holder to the left of the toilet
Pick up the roll from the holder
Move to the front of the toilet to the right of you
Place the roll in the closet cabinet
Move to the toilet ahead of you
Pick up the roll from the toilet
Move to the front of the toilet ahead of you
Place the roll in the closet cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put two toilet paper rolls in the cabinet closest to the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the toilet paper holder to the left of the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper from the toilet paper holder.
Turn around and walk to the cabinet below the sink.
Place the toilet paper in the leftmost cabinet under the sink.
Walk to the tube on top of the toilet.
Pick up the tube on top of the toilet.
Walk to the cabinets below the sink.
Place the tube in the leftmost cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a tube and a roll of toilet paper in the leftmost cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the toilet, then turn left and look down.
Take the toilet paper roll off of the toilet paper holder.
Turn left and walk towards the shower, then turn left again and walk towards the wall, turn left again to face the toilet.
Open the leftmost cabinet door below the sink and put the toilet paper roll inside, then close the door.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left and walk up to the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper roll off of the toilet tank.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and take a step forward, turn right again to face the toilet.
Open the leftmost cabinet door and place the toilet paper roll inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Move two toilet paper rolls into a cabinet.
